snippet.title: Card Hog Gameplay
snippet.description:
Available on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1163740/Card_Hog/

Pig-based dungeon crawler packed with weird creatures, powerful weapons, magical shenanigans and loads of exciting card combinations!
